Privacy PolicyWho we are

Our website address is: http://annemiekdebruin.nl.
For more information about Annemiek de Bruin, see her biography.

What personal information we collect

We do not actively collect any personal information.

Feedback

Only when you give feedback (on the Home page) will your name and e-mail address be registered, to respond to your feedback.

Statistics

For every page you visit an extra request will be made, this way we know which pages are visited. Through this request will also be determined what country you are in. This is standard WordPress (privacy policy) functionality.

Contact

Any questions or comments may be sent to info@annemiekdebruin.nl.
